# 🧠 Exam System

A modern web-based exam management system that allows teachers to create, manage, and organize exams, while students can participate and track their progress.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Create and manage question banks
* Organize exams with multiple questions
* Clean and responsive user interface
* Real-time interaction with the system
* Role-based structure (Teacher / Student) *(if implemented)*

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

* **Frontend:** Next.js, React, TypeScript
* **Styling:** Tailwind CSS, ShadCN UI
* **State Management:** React Context / Hooks
* **Backend / Services:** Firebase *(if used)*

