## ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Yazan-kass/exam-system.git
cd exam-system
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Run the development server:

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

## 🔑 Environment Variables

Create a `.env.local` file and add:

```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_KEY=your_key
NEXT_PUBLIC_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_domain
```

*(Update based on your actual config — especially if using Firebase)*

